<br>
His armor flickered with the lantern light that cascaded across the room. His spurs chirped as he made his way across the way and sat at a lonely table out of the way a bit by the hearth. He stopped and looked around at the inhabitants wondering from where they had all traveled from and what had brought them all from so far away or what ventures they might have all told.<br>
<br>
It was then he felt a tapping on his shoulder and a comely lass asking what he might have to drink. He looked up and smiled broadly past tired eyes, &quot;milk&quot;.<br>
<br>
There was undoubtedly silence followed by some rather abrupt laughter which then again rescinded to the bustle of the tavern. He chuckled softly to himself as he leaned back easing the weight of his armor to take a long needed rest in the warm confines of the tavern. <p>Banegrivm Shadowblight<br>Sovereign Lord of the 1st Fist of Light<br>www.1stfistoflight.com</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/udrixa.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Drixa</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Barmaid</span><br>  Posts: 21<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(10/18/01 12:10:20 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=14.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: *walks in*</span><hr size=1> Aye, if it's milk  yer're wanting, I can deliver it quickly for you... I also have stronger  spirits which I'm sure may quench the thirst of a mighty warrior... <p>Drixa<BR>
