<br>
&quot;Hail M'Lord!&quot; She greets him, bowing deeply. The wood elf straigtens and gives the paladin a bawdy wink. &quot;I see that you are enjoying..&quot; She glances into his glass and simply cannot suppress her mirth. &quot;MILK??&quot; She chuckles. The lady turns and calls out to the barmaid. &quot;I'll have what he's having!&quot; She states with a grin then raises her hands and performs intricate arcane movements. She promtly rises off of the floor several feet and moves over to stand next to Bane's table. Sitting in a cross-legged position she hovers exactly at table level, able to rest her elbows on it's surface. &quot;How do you fare, M'lord?&quot; She enquires with a bright smile.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ujape2lions.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jape2Lions</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 42<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(11/28/01 1:29:26 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=14.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: *walks in*</span><hr size=1> I'll have anything other than what's he's having.<br>
